snippet.title: Downhill Legend Gameplay-Trailer [official]
snippet.description:
BE LEGENDARY! 

This is Arcade Gaming that gets ur b*** movin’!
https://downhill-legend.com/


Join the ARCARDIO ADVENTURE of SisyFox and become a LEGEND! 
Make your steps count and get in those little exercises each and every day!

Dive into a hypnotic ride down beautiful mountains to get SisyFox fit again.
Earn rewards for every step you take in real life to equip yourself and aim for the top of the global leaderboard!



On top of that: visit the real SisyFox-Arcade console, the biggest game-controller in the world, to get trophies and exclusive skins :D


So what are you waiting for? Get DOWNHILL LEGEND now for free!
